## DOCUMENTATION UPDATE RULES

When Claude Code discovers something new about FCS:

### Add to FCS_SystemReference.md:
- New system behavior discovered
- New exact function names found
- New component names found
- Corrections to existing documentation

### Add to KnownIssues.md:
- Any crash and its fix
- Any workaround for broken functionality
- Any FCS behavior that differs from expectation
- Format: always add newest issues at TOP of file

### Add to FCS_Blueprints/[Folder].md:
- New asset discovered in that folder
- Deeper understanding of existing asset
- GodOfRuin relevance updated

### Create new Systems/ doc when:
- A new custom Blueprint is built
- A new FCS system is extended
- A new integration pattern is established

