## PARAGON CHARACTER IMPORT RULES

Never deviate from these:

1. Max 2-3 characters per session
2. Always use FCS Manny skeleton:
   `/Game/FlexibleCombatSystem/GASP/UEFN-Manny/Meshes/SK_UEFN_Mannequin.SK_UEFN_Mannequin`
3. Import at START of session before building
4. Verify animations work before building level content
5. Create BP_AI_Parent child immediately after import
6. Test in PIE before marking import complete
7. Update docs/Assets/ParagonCharacters.md after each import

If import crashes UE5: this is RED escalation.
Stop. Do not retry. Report to Eric.

