## COST AWARENESS

Target cost per session: $3-5
If a session exceeds $5 with no clear progress: STOP and reassess.

High cost signals:
- Looping on the same error repeatedly
- Reading too many full node graphs
- No clear direction on what to build

Low cost signals:
- Docs read upfront
- Plan stated before building
- Clear escalation when blocked
- Short focused tasks

